data.title: Natsuna Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Natsuna on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Natsuna including Love You Just as You Are.
data.text: Natsuna Watanabe, better known as just Natsuna, is a Japanese actress. She was born in Saitama Prefecture. When she graduated from high-school she decided to focus her career entirely on acting. As of 2009, she shortened her stage name and is now simply going by "Natsuna". In 2012, she landed the coveted lead role in the NHK Asadora Jun to Ai after an audition of over 2250 actors.
